  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are an Earworm.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are an underworld contractor who hacks memories for a living. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the memories of your victims in order to unlock the security questions to their bank account. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A pyschedelic first person thriller experience with some basic puzzle elements. This is a short game, roughly 30-40 minutes long and designed to be completed in one sitting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2765340/extras/7f2b0abe4db7211a31dca01403e4a7f7.poster.avif?t=1745327292\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2765340/extras/7f2b0abe4db7211a31dca01403e4a7f7.webm?t=1745327292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thumping 90s techno soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles to hack your victim's bank account</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore unique memories </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are an Earworm.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are an underworld contractor who hacks memories for a living. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the memories of your victims in order to unlock the security questions to their bank account. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A pyschedelic first person thriller experience with some basic puzzle elements. This is a short game, roughly 30-40 minutes long and designed to be completed in one sitting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2765340/extras/7f2b0abe4db7211a31dca01403e4a7f7.poster.avif?t=1745327292\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2765340/extras/7f2b0abe4db7211a31dca01403e4a7f7.webm?t=1745327292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thumping 90s techno soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles to hack your victim's bank account</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore unique memories </p></li></ul>",
